    <briefdescription>
<para>Driver for the TA6586 dual H-bridge motor driver. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Pinout: <verbatim>*       TA-6586
*       -------
*  5 - |       | - VCC
*  6 - |       | - GND
*  7 - |       | - FI (Forward pin)
*  8 - |   _   | - BI (Backward pin)
*       --/ \--
* </verbatim></para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kForwardPin</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>PWM pin connected to FI (forward input) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kBackwardPin</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>PWM pin connected to BI (backward input) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
